criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. comparative studies;

          2. adult patients (> 18 years) with NLDO undergoing primary or revision EN-DCR;

          3. all studies included were required to provide the success rates of both MMC and
             control groups, and the followed up time was more than 6 months.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. studies which did not provide the success rates;

          2. studies which included pediatric cases.
